sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / API Client
    participant LSD as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as GarakInlineEvalAdapter
    participant Remote as GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
    participant Garak as garak subprocess
    participant KFP as KFP API (DSPA)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pod (garak)
    participant LLM as Target LLM (vLLM)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FilesAPI as Llama Stack Files API
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant EvalHub as Eval-Hub Service
    participant Adapter as GarakAdapter Pod
    participant Sidecar as Eval-Hub Sidecar<br/>localhost HTTP
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,FilesAPI: Flow 1: Inline Garak Scan (Llama Stack)

    User->>LSD: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LSD->>Inline: dispatch to inline provider
    Inline->>Garak: spawn subprocess<br/>(os.setsid, semaphore-gated)
    Garak->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    LLM-->>Garak: Probe responses
    Garak-->>Inline: Exit code + scan results
    Inline->>FilesAPI: Upload reports (in-process)
    Inline-->>LSD: Job status + results
    LSD-->>User: eval.jobs.status / retrieve

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Remote KFP Garak Scan (Llama Stack)

    User->>LSD: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LSD->>Remote: dispatch to remote provider
    Remote->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Bearer Token
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pod
    KFPPod->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    LLM-->>KFPPod: Probe responses
    KFPPod->>FilesAPI: Upload results<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    Remote-->>LSD: Poll KFP status
    LSD-->>User: eval.jobs.status / retrieve

    Note over EvalHub,MLflow: Flow 3: Eval-Hub Simple Mode

    EvalHub->>Adapter: K8s Job creation<br/>ConfigMap mount /meta/job.json
    Adapter->>Garak: spawn subprocess
    Garak->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    LLM-->>Garak: Probe responses
    Garak-->>Adapter: Scan results
    Adapter->>OCI: Push artifact bundle<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Registry creds
    Adapter->>MLflow: Log metrics + artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Report completion<br/>HTTP localhost

    Note over EvalHub,S3: Flow 4: Eval-Hub KFP Mode

    EvalHub->>Adapter: K8s Job creation<br/>ConfigMap mount /meta/job.json
    Adapter->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Bearer Token
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pod
    KFPPod->>LLM: Probes<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    KFPPod->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    Adapter->>KFP: Poll status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    Adapter->>OCI: Push bundle<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Adapter->>MLflow: Log metrics<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Adapter->>Sidecar: Report completion<br/>HTTP localhost

    Note over KFPPod,S3: Flow 5: Intents Benchmark Pipeline (KFP - 6 Steps)

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        KFPPod->>KFPPod: Step 1: validate (garak import check)
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 2: resolve_taxonomy<br/>HTTPS 443 / AWS IAM
        KFPPod->>LLM: Step 3: sdg_generate<br/>HTTPS 443 / SDG_API_KEY
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 4: prepare_prompts<br/>Upload CSVs / AWS IAM
        KFPPod->>LLM: Step 5: garak_scan<br/>HTTPS 443 / Bearer Token
        Note right of KFPPod: 5a: Attacker Model (TAP)<br/>5b: Judge Model<br/>5c: Evaluator Model
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 6: write_kfp_outputs<br/>HTTPS 443 / AWS IAM
    end
